+# The Time Capsule build links rpcd_classic as a static nonshared helper.
+# rpcd_classic also depends on smbd_base, and smbd_base already includes
+# rpc_ncacn_np.c for smbd's named-pipe path. Keep RPC_NCACN_NP as the policy
+# handle provider needed by the RPC services, but do not pull rpc_ncacn_np.c
+# into the helper target a second time or waf rejects it before linking due
+# duplicate source ownership.
